@startuml 03-rag-architecture
title Kien truc RAG - Ingestion & Retrieval theo tung domain
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

package "Ingestion Pipeline (offline / batch)" {
  [S3: raw-documents\n(quy dinh noi bo, van ban phap luat,\nchinh sach tin dung, huong dan dinh gia...)] as S3RAW
  [Chunking + Embedding Job\n(Lambda/batch, goi Omnirouter\nembeddings endpoint)] as EMBED_JOB
  database "Aurora PostgreSQL + pgvector\n(namespace theo domain:\nlegal_kb, financial_kb, collateral_kb,\ncompliance_kb, scoring_kb)" as VDB
  S3RAW --> EMBED_JOB
  EMBED_JOB --> VDB : upsert vectors
}

package "Retrieval (runtime, moi luot goi Agent)" {
  [Agent (LlmAgent)] as AGENT
  [Retriever Tool] as RETRIEVER
  [Omnirouter\n(embeddings API)] as ROUTER_EMB
  AGENT --> RETRIEVER : query
  RETRIEVER --> ROUTER_EMB : embed(query)
  ROUTER_EMB --> RETRIEVER : query_vector
  RETRIEVER --> VDB : similarity search\n(top-k, filter theo domain)
  VDB --> RETRIEVER : matched chunks
  RETRIEVER --> AGENT : context injection
}

EMBED_JOB ..> ROUTER_EMB : embed(chunks)

note bottom
  Moi Agent chuyen biet (Legal/Financial/Collateral/
  Compliance/Scoring) co retriever tool rieng, chi truy
  van namespace/schema tuong ung domain cua no - tranh
  "context leakage" giua cac domain khac nhau.
end note

@enduml
